10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5o3BDFz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5o3BDFz.gif&h=d04004f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3734605fb9fede693d5b90bb79ac6034b3bcf237","tid":2445360,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"關科興咩事呢"},{"pid":"07611fa888d3f41669853004295313960df9f972","tid":2445360,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2597e63053914939aad5a0ccb0ac8146f919b41b","tid":2445360,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"幾時追上感染死亡人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"為国捐軀 好光榮架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d6d626a6225e345051682fbb7c8959a70f146b","tid":2445360,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"兩名曾經接種科興疫苗的男子下午離世。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署表示，接獲醫管局通知，一名在本月7日，在明愛醫院深切治療部接受治療的80歲男子，及後轉送瑪嘉烈醫院深切治療部接受進一步治療，下午因缺血性腸道疾病離世。<br />\n<br />\n另一名前日在廣華醫院深切治療部接受治療的67歲男子，亦在下午離世。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名本身患有心房顫動、心臟衰竭、紅血球過多及酒精性脂肪肝的63歲男子，本星期二接種科興疫苗，翌日開始感到身體虛弱，今日情況轉差並前往北區醫院急症室求醫。<br />\n<br />\n男子轉送深切治療部接受進一步治療，初步診斷為急性中風，現時情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，他在沙田源禾路體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種科興疫苗，逗留在接種中心觀察，期間並沒有不適紀錄。"},{"pid":"7c0718b1a01841ebde63d148466c7cbdfe9638bf","tid":2445360,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5963d1900b4973b42590fc9ace6ccc7b4ba2a81","tid":2445360,"uid":361751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bu760TE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBu760TE.png&h=a9714012&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"